    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><p class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">A color wheel is really just the spectrum twisted around so that the violet and red ends are joined. This wheel is particularly useful for showing how the colors relate to each other and how you can create new ones by mixing two or more of them.</p></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="image3 cid-tt612oXwA9" id="image3-5" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
